title: Kenya Google to Invest Sh4 Billion in Lake Turkana Wind Power Project
text:
Kenya: Google to Invest Sh4 Billion in Lake Turkana Wind Power Project 
All Africa Thursday 22nd October, 2015 
Google has said it will invest up to Sh4 billion in a wind power project, expected to generate 310MW of clean energy, at Loiyangalani, Marsabit county.
